  "title": "Architectural Coordinator",
  "description": "<p><u>Responsibility:</u></p>\n<p>-Conduct Subcontractor co-ordination meeting.</p>\n<p>-Attend Consultant meeting.</p>\n<p>-Supervise site project team.</p>\n<p>-Schedule, monitor and supervise the overal progress of site work.</p>\n<p>-Assist Senior Project Manager in planning, controlling and co-ordination of subcontractor's work.</p>\n<p>-Knowledge with local code of practice, i.e R.I inspection, TOP application, CSC and Final Completion.</p>\n<p>-Knowledge of Autocad software application and basic drafting.</p>\n<p><u>Requirements:</u></p>\n<p>-Degree/ Diploma in Civil Engineering or Building</p>\n<p>-Familar with all stages of construction activities</p>",
